<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Provost" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Provost,</orth> the keeper of a prison, a gaoler: <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.118" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 118</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.4.73" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.177" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 177</bibl> and passim in this play.
